sources.description:
Earthsea Part ONE: In the magical world of Earthsea, the Amulet of Peace has ensured harmony between humans and dragons for centuries. But when the Amulet is broken and a piece of it disappears, it’s up to a neophyte wizard to restore balance and stop a nefarious king from conquering Earthsea’s islands.
